{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went-- I went back to Sweden, just for a year, until '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was working in the trade department in Stockholm, and the-- with the Hungarians, with the trade between Hungary and Sweden, which-- The result of that was that I was transferred into-- to Budapest in November '42.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was transferred, because they thought that I was now experienced, in this field, in this commercial field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my job was to go on and take up negotiations with the Hungarians about the exchange of goods and trade.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We bought very much of foodstuff, at that time, from Hungary, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we-- we exported our steel and those products, ball bearings and all that, to them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a regular trade negotiations, exchange of goods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I lived in a-- in a-- on the-- on the Buda-- on the Buda side of of-- of Budapest, on the hills, down there, near the Gellert Hotel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- And interesting enough, I-- I rented it by-- from a-- an-- an-- a Hungarian-Jewish businessman, Manfred Weiss, who was one of the big-- big industrialists at that time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They owned factories and all that in-- in Budapest at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I rented part of his house on-- on that slope up to-- above Gellert Hotel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't married, at the time, in '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went home, in-- in '43, where we have the-- the wedding, in Stockholm, in June of '43.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my wife then went back, with me, to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- then we had this one-- let's say it was one-- little more than one year together in Budapest, when I then, later on, found that it was impossible to keep the family.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
